                </TextRuns>
                <Style />
              </Paragraph>
              <Paragraph>
                <TextRuns>
                  <TextRun>
                    <Value>This accounting includes disclosures of protected health information made during the six (6) years prior to the request date, excluding disclosures made before April 14, 2003, in accordance with HIPAA Privacy Rule 45 CFR §164.528. Disclosures for treatment, payment, and healthcare operations (TPO), disclosures to the patient, disclosures authorized in writing by the patient, and incidental disclosures are not included in this accounting.</Value>
                    <Style>
                      <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                      <FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily>
                      <FontSize>11pt</FontSize>
                      <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                      <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                      <Color>#000000</Color>
